data.name: notifyIcon_vDesk.BalloonTipText
data.value:
Virtual Desk Switch has been started. A black icon with a white number should be displayed in the notification area near the clock.
If the icon isn't visible, please check the hidden notification icons by clicking the (^) arrow next to the notification area. If you find the icon in the hidden area, drag & drop it with your mouse to the area near the clock.
